OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOccasional
OL,6,Fsunny spells this evening but a cloudy
OL,7,Fend to the day for many. An increasing
OL,8,Fchance of showers overnight, but in
OL,9,Fany clearer periods temperatures may
OL,10,Fdip low enough to give a touch of
OL,11,Fgrass frost in the countryside.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA cloudy start for most
OL,14,Fwith the odd shower. Brightening up
OL,15,Ffor some by the afternoon but heavy
OL,16,Fslow-moving showers may develop across
OL,17,FPembrokeshire and Carmarthenshire.
OL,18,FFeeling somewhat cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
